    {
      "id": "2d6e0ee8-ca98-406a-9062-40549ee6ceb0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Planning is core self-regulated learning skill. There is a lack of studies that focuses on the contents of planning and the feature is usually assessed on the effects of planning. Authors perform a qualitative analysis of 650 learner plans from 15 MOOCs.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "2d6e0ee8-ca98-406a-9062-40549ee6ceb0",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
