    {
      "id": "626e3b0a-6079-44c2-b9a3-5949f6398f3a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors start with identifcation of planning tactics and mapped which planning tactics lead to course completion. Learners whose plans specify specific times of day are more likely to complete the MOOC event though only 25% of students engaged in this tactic.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "626e3b0a-6079-44c2-b9a3-5949f6398f3a",
